N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 2608.4 - Notification

State Regulations
(a) The
commissioner shall notify the company in writing as to the status of the
reapplication. (b) The commissioner
shall render one of the following decisions: (1)
approved as submitted; (2)
approved conditionally; (3)
approved with probation; or
(4)
defunded. Notes
